quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Swaad, (Insiguro y’iyi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwayo bwose buzi Imana yonyene gusa). Ndarahiye kuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu ifise ubutumwa nyakuri"
  38,2,Mugabo abahakanye Umuremyi wabo bari mu bishima nugu higanwa
  38,3,"Twahoneje abantu bangahe imbere yabo, batako bakoma induru mugabo umwanya w’ukurokoka wamaze guhera"
  38,4,"Baratangaye mugihe bashikirwa n’uwutuza ava muribo hanyuma abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuze bati:- uyo muntu n’umurozi kandi n’umubeshi"
  38,5,"Yagize Imana zose kuba ari Imana imwe gusa, ntankeka iri n’ijambo ry’igitangaza"
  38,6,"Baciye bitahira bamwe mubakuru babo bavuga bati:- nimwigire kandi mwigumanire n’izo Mana zanyu, mu vy’ukuri iri n’ijambo rikenewe"
  38,7,"Twebwe ntitwigeze twumva ibi bintu yuko muri iyi migenzo yacu yanyuma, kandi ntivyamye ho ibi vyose atari uko ari ivyadutse gusa"
  38,8,"Niwe wenyene yamanuriwe ubu butumire gusa natwe ntitwabuhabwa, mugabo abo bantu bari bafise amakenga gusa kubera ubutumire bwanje, ahubwo ntibara honja ibihano vyanje"
  38,9,"Mbega barafise ububiko bw’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, nyene ubushobozi atanga vyose"
  38,10,"Canke barafise ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo, rero nibafate inzira ibashikana yo"
  38,11,Izi n’ingabo zizo gendeshwa ningoga muvyondo vy’abahakanyi vyagendeshejwe ningoga aho hambere
  38,12,Abaho hambere barahakanye abantu bo kuntumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) nabo kuntumwa y’Imana Aadi (iii) na Fir’auni nyene amazu y’inkingi zikoma komeye
  38,13,Na Thamuda hamwe n’abantu bokwa Lutwi n’abantu bo mukibira c’ibiti vyinshi iyo niyo mirwi yabo
  38,14,"Abo bose bara hakanye intumwa z’Imana, rero ibihano vyanje vyaraba shikiye"
  38,15,N’aba ntibarindira atari akaruru kamwe gusa kukuzurwa kwabo kata rindiriza
  38,16,"Bama bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, nutuzanire bimwe mubihano vyacu imbere yuwo musi wugu harurwa"
  38,17,"Nutenyenye kuri ivyo bavuga, mugabo wibuke wa muntu wacu mweranda ariwe Daudi (iii) nyene inguvu, mu vy’ukuri yari umuntu agaruka ku Mana n’ubu gamburutsi"
  38,18,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twara gamburukiye imisozi hamwe nawe ininahaze kuva k’umugoroba no mugitondo
  38,19,Hamwe n’inyoni zegereranijwe hamwe n’izindi zose zara mugamburukira
  38,20,Duca dushira mubwami bwiwe ubushobozi nukumuha ubumenyi bw’ugucira imanza abantu
  38,21,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru z’abari mumatati baca basimbira mucumba c’intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii)
  38,22,"Mugihe binjira kwa Daudi (iii) yarabatinye nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntutinye kuri twebwe turi mumatati, umwe muri twebwe yarahemukiye mugenzi wiwe, none nuducire urubanza rw’ukuri, kandi ntuhengame ahanaka kandi uturongore munzira igororotse"
  38,23,"Mu vy’ukuri uyu ni mwene wanje, afise intama z’inyana mirongo icenda n’icenda, nanje nkaba mfise inyana imwe gusa mugabo yavuze ati ndamuhe iyi rwanje ayitungire, none yananiye mu majambo"
  38,24,"Avuga ati:- ni vy’ukuri yaguhemukiye mukugusaba iyo ntungwa yawe mukwongereza kuntungwa ziwe, ntankeka abari mw’ishirahamwe benshi bama bahemukirana bamwe kubandi dukuyemwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, nabo bantu bari kurushi, mu mwanya intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) yabona yuko twamuhaye ikibazo, aca asaba ikigongwe ku Muremyi wiwe n’ugupfukama n’ubwitonzi ntangere nugu tumbera ku Muremyi wiwe"
  38,25,"Duca tumugirira ikigongwe kuri ivyo vyose, mu vy’ukuri arafise kuri twebwe icubahiro kininiya n’ahantu heza"
  38,26,"Ewe Daudi (iii) mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaguhaye ubutegetsi ng’aha kw’Isi, rero nubacire abo bantu urubanza rw’ukuri kandi ntukurikire ivyo umutima wawe ushatse ntuze ukuzimize munzira nziza y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri bamwe bazimira nuguta inzira y’Imana abo bantu bazoronka ibihano bikaze cane kubera ukwibagira kwabo wa musi wuguharurwa"
  38,27,"Kandi twebwe ntitwaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose kubusa gusa, ibi vyose nivyo bikeka bamwe batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri, rero ibihano bikaze cane vy’umuriro udahera bizoba shikira bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  38,28,"Mbega tubagire bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza yuko boba bangana n’abononyi bagira ubwo bwononyi ng’aha kw’Isi, canke tubagire aba gamburukira Imana ko bangana n’abononyi"
  38,29,"Iki gitabu twakimanuye kuri wewe, kikaba gifise imihezagiro myinshi cane kugira ngo abantu bategere neza, iyumvire amajambo yaco hamwe n’abafise ubwenge nabo bategere neza"
  38,30,"Twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) ikibondo citwa Suleymanu (iii) akaba yari mu bantu beza, kandi akaba yari afise n’ubwitonzi ntangere"
  38,31,Mugihe bwagoroba yashikirijwe Ifarasi zihumuye zihagaze nazo zikaba zari zihwahutse mugihe zitegetswe kwiruka
  38,32,"Yaciye avuga ati:- jewe nkunda ibintu vyiza mukwibuka Umuremyi wanje, mu nyuma zafarasi zinyegeza inyuma y’uruzitiro"
  38,33,"Nimu bagarure iwanje, hanyuma aca atangura kuzi hanagura kumaguru yazo no kumazosi yazo"
  38,34,Twaramuhaye intumwa y’Imana Suleymanu (iii) duca dushiraho uwundi mubiri hejuru y’inyegamo yiwe hanyuma aragaruka wenyene
  38,35,"Aca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, nungirire ikigongwe kandi umpe n’ubwami, kandi ntuze ubuhe uwariwe wese munyuma zanje, ntankeka ni wewe mutanzi wa vyose"
  38,36,"Duca tumu gamburukiza umuyaga ugenda buhoro buhoro kw’itegeko ryiwe, naho ushaka gushika hose"
  38,37,Hamwe n’ibisigo n’abubatsi n’abibira mumazi
  38,38,N’ibindi bisigo biboshwe n’iminyororo
  38,39,"Iyi n’ingabirano yacu twaguhaye tutarinze guharurirana, rero nuyitange canke uyigumye utarinze kugiriranira ibiharuro"
  38,40,Mu vy’ukuri arafise kuri twebwe icubahiro n’ahantu heza
  38,41,"Kandi mwibuke intumwa yacu y’Imana Ayyubu (iii) mugihe Umuremyi wiwe yamuhamagara avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri Shetani yanshikirije ibishoboka hamwe n’ingorane"
  38,42,"Ihute nuku kuguru kwawe, naya niyo mazi apfuse yukwisukira hamwe n’ayandi yukunywa"
  38,43,Duca tumuha abantu biwe hamwe n’abandi nkabo hamwe nabo kumigisha ivuye iwacu hamwe n’ubutumwa ku bantu bafise ubwenge
  38,44,"Nufate amasonga y’uduti mukuboko kwawe, hunyuma uce umukubitisha umucance wawe, kandi ntute indahiro yawe, ntankeka twebwe twamusanze ari mu bantu batekereje kandi n’intore, mu vy’ukuri yari muba gamburutsi bacane"
  38,45,Bibuke abantu bacu ariyo ntumwa yacu y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) na Is’haqa n’intumwa y’Imana na Yaaqubu bari bafise ubushobozi n’ubwenge buhagije
  38,46,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twagutoye kuri ryajambo ryiza cane ryukwibuka umusi w’imperuka
  38,47,"Kandi ntankeka abamyeho imbere yacu, nabo nimu bantu beza batowe"
  38,48,Kandi mwibuke intumwa y’Imana Ismaaili (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Al’yasaa (iii) n’intumwa y’Imana Dhul’qiflu (iii) n’abo bose bari mu bantu b’intungane
  38,49,Ubu n’ubwibutso mu vy’ukuri abatinya Imana yabo y’ukuri igituro cabo caho bazo garukira hazoba heza cane
  38,50,Imirima yukwicara mwo mubuzima bwabo bwose izoba yuguruye imiryango yayo kubera bo gusa
  38,51,Bazo kwegamira kunyegamo basaba ivyamwa vyinshi hamwe n’ibinyobwa
  38,52,Hamwe nabo bazoba ho n’abanega babo bahumurije amaso yabo kubatambukanyi babo
  38,53,Ibi nivyo mwaraganiwe k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,54,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo migisha yacu idahera
  38,55,Nuko rero mu vy’ukuri bamwe barenga imbibe ingaruka zabo zizoba ziri ahantu habi cane
  38,56,Wamuriro witiriwe Jahannamu niwo bazokwinjiramwo naho nahateguwe nabi cane
  38,57,N’uku bizoba rero nibahonje amazi y’amarike n’amashira
  38,58,N’ibindi bihano nk’ibi ni vyinshi
  38,59,"Izi nizo ngabo zizo kwinjira hamwe namwe, mugabo ntizaronse ahantu heza zishikira mugabo zizo kwinjira mu muriro udahera"
  38,60,"Bavuze bati:- mwebwe ntakaze ryiza mufise mwebwe nimwe mwatumye turonka ibihano aho naho n’ahantu h’ubwicaro bubi cane"
  38,61,"Bavuze bati:- Muremyi wacu, abatumye tugira ibi vyose, n’ubongereze ibihano vy’incuro zibiri iyo mu muriro udahera"
  38,62,"Bazovuga\tbati:-\tvyabaye\tgute\tko\ttutababona\tbabantu\ttwahora tubaharura ko bari mu bantu babi"
  38,63,Erega twaraba kengereye mugabo amaso yacu ntiyababona gusa
  38,64,Ntankeka ibi bintu vy’amatati y’abantu bo mumuriro udahera nay’ukuri
  38,65,"Vuga\tuti:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tjewe\tnd’uwutuza\tgusa,\tkandi\tntayindi\tMana itegerezwa gusengwa atariyo yonyene rudende nyene ubushobozi"
  38,66,Umumenyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibirimwo vyose nyene ubushobozi hamwe n’ikigongwe cinshi
  38,67,"Vuga uti:- izi n’inkuru zihambaye cane"
  38,68,Mutitayeho namba
  38,69,Ntabumenyi nari mfise bw’ibiremwa bitagatifu mugihe batumvikana
  38,70,Simbwirwa ikintu na kimwe kuri jewe atari uko nd’umuntu atuza abantu kandi mboneka
  38,71,"Umuremyi wawe mugihe yababwira Abamarayika ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzorema umuntu ndamukuye mw’ivu"
  38,72,"Ninarangiza kurema uyo muntu nukumu huhera umutima uvuye\tkuri jewe, rero nimuce mumupfukamira nukumu gamburukira"
  38,73,Bara gamburutse Abamarayika bose uko bangana bose
  38,74,Dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi yishimye nukuba muba hakanyi b’Imana
  38,75,"Imana yamubwiye iti:- ewe Ibilisi, n’igiki cakubujje ku gamburukira uwo naremye ku maboko yanje, mbega winamuye canke wabaye mubantu bakuru"
  38,76,"Nawe yishura ati:- jewe ndimwiza gusumba uyo waremye, kuko jewe wandemye unkuye mu muriro udahera, nawe umurema umukuye mw’ivu"
  38,77,"Imana\tica\tivuga\titi:-\tnuve\tmuri\tuwo\tmuriro\tudahera\tkuko\turamaze gutabwa kure n’imigisha yanje"
  38,78,Mu vy’ukuri umuvumo wanje uzoba hejuru yawe kuri kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,79,"Nawe yishura ati:- Muremyi wanje, numpe umwanya na mutoyi gusa kugeza k’umusi bazozurwa ibiremwa vyose"
  38,80,"Imana imubwira iti:- nivyo wewe uri mubaronse ikibanza c’ukubaho"
  38,81,Kugeza kumwanya w’umusi wategekanijwe
  38,82,"Nawe yishura ati:- ndarahiye k’ukuri kw’iteka ryawe ntankeka jewe abo bantu bawe nzobazimiza uko bangana bose"
  38,83,Dukuye mwo ba bantu bawe muribo ar’intore
  38,84,"Imana ivuga iti:- ndarahiye mvugishije ukuri"
  38,85,Mu vy’ukuri jewe nzokwuzuza mu muriro udahera kuri wewe Shetani hamwe n’abagu kurikira muribo
  38,86,"Vuga uti:- jewe sindaba saba impembo kuri ibi, kandi jewe sindi mu bantu bitegeka"
  38,87,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ubutumwa ku bantu bose
  38,88,Kandi ntankeka mwebwe muzomenya inkuru ziwe mumwanya